videos.headline: Barkley has high praise for Nashville, Melrose
videos.description: Charles Barkley joins Steve Levy and Barry Melrose to discuss NBA cities that bring the same passion as the hockey fans in Nashville and why he's such a big fan of Melrose.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NHL Interview (Barkley has high praise for Nashville, Melrose) 2017/06/05

videos.headline: Subban not surprised by Preds tying series
videos.description: P.K. Subban discusses the Predators' confidence in evening the Stanley Cup Final after falling behind 2-0 and what's behind Nashville's stellar defensemen group.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NHL Interview (Subban not surprised by Preds tying series) 2017/06/05

videos.headline: Subban talks bad breath
videos.description: P.K. Subban speaks to Steve Levy and Barry Melrose about the respect he has for Sidney Crosby and his diet that could potentially lead to having bad breath.

videos.headline: Melrose says Predators have the luck now
videos.description: After Nashville ties up the Stanley Cup Final with Pittsburgh, Steve Levy and Barry Melrose break down how much an evenly matched series it is.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NHL Analysis (Melrose says Predators have the luck now) 2017/06/05 SC
